# Custom C++ Game SDK

A clean, engine-agnostic C++ SDK inspired by Source-style APIs.

## Features
- Plugin system (DLL / SO)
- Lua scripting support
- Tick / frame callbacks
- Basic ECS architecture
- No engine dependency

## Goals
- Modding support
- Scriptable gameplay logic
- Extendable SDK core

## Roadmap
- Rendering hooks
- Input system
- Networking layer
